import System.IO


main :: IO ()
main = do
    first_temp <- getLine
    let first_t = words first_temp
    let first = read $ first_t!!0 :: Int
    let last = read $ first_t!!1 :: Int
    -- your code goes here

getMultipleLines :: Int -> IO [String]

getMultipleLines n
    | n <= 0 = return []
    | otherwise = do          
        x <- getLine         
        xs <- getMultipleLines (n-1)    
        let ret = (x:xs)    
        return ret
